; line-height: 18px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">|</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">思维导图的水平思考能够提供没有任何限制的</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">360</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">°自由联想，结合“多角度思考”训练，能够让大脑更加有创意；</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: normal;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; 