x; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">|</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">思维导图不仅有自由联想，还可以和结构化思维和金字塔原理结合起来，有效地梳理大脑逻辑，让表达更高效；</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: normal;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">3</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">）</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; paddin