it; line-height: 18px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">911</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">悲剧后，这家公司广泛的运用思维导图做为规划、组织的工具，成功完成重建曼哈顿的任务。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: normal;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">l&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">新加坡、韩国政府已将思维导图列为学校必修课；</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: normal;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">l&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">菲律宾创办一所思维导图专门学校，以思维导图法教授各个学科……</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: normal;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">l&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-hi