font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; color: red;">必先利其器</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: normal;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">Ø&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer;">如今的商业社会，大到一个严谨的项目计划需要有系统的、创新的思维；</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: normal;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 18px; font-family: inh